Mythaphil is the major region of a lush jungle planet sharing the same name.

Once filled with civilization, Mythaphil is now nothing but overgrown vegetation and wildlife. Underneath the layers of plants lies the synthetic infrastructure of the world that used to be.

In its current state, Mythaphil is a relatively safe planet. It supports a few million sentient inhabitants who have resorted to a primitive, but comfortable lifestyle. Among its small population, Di has been seen conducting what appears to be research in the last city of the planet.
